-- Author Vince Gennaro Discusses `the End of Steroid Era' (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-07-26T12:35:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-26/author-vince-gennaro-discusses-the-end-of-steroid-era-audio-.html
Vince Gennaro, author of "Diamond 
Dollars: The Economics of Winning in Baseball," says it could be
the "beginning of the end" of steroid use in Major League 
Baseball. He also discusses New York Yankee player Alex 
Rodriguez. Gennaro talks with Bloomberg's  Tom Keene  and Sara 
Eisen on Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg Surveillance."      (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:49
 